I want to study social work to help children who are abused or neglected and to help troubled families. I want to work for the Division of Family and Children Services. I have some important values for social work: service, respect, and a commitment to helping others. I also want to be a good person and improve my skills to help people better. These values are important for social workers and for me.

I have always wanted to help people. In school, I saw people with problems who did not get help. Some people used bad ways to deal with their problems. I wanted to find a way to help. I studied psychology in college. After I graduated from Piedmont College in 2009, I took a break. One day, a friend told me about a 16-year-old boy who was living with his abusive parents. The boy was scared and wanted to leave. I went to the police and told them my concerns. I said I studied psychology and could help. The police asked me to talk to the parents. They said their son was bad and used excuses to blame him. After that, I decided to become a social worker to help children with family problems.

I also care about social justice. We say that every person is important, but we often do the same things as others. I do not want to be like everyone else. I want to be myself. In school, I stood up for what I believe in. I wore what I wanted, colored my hair, and spoke out against racism and injustice. I will continue to stand up for what is right.

This paper talks about two models that help us understand a sleep problem called insomnia. The biological model looks at how genetics and medical reasons can cause insomnia. The sociocultural model looks at how the environment and social factors affect insomnia.

The biological model says that insomnia can be caused by genetic information and medical problems. The sociocultural model says that environmental factors like race, ethnicity, and economic status can also cause insomnia.

This paper will look at some research that relates to these two models. We will explain each study and its findings. Then we will talk about the strengths and weaknesses of each study.

Insomnia is a sleep problem. It can be caused by different things. One type of insomnia is a primary sleep disorder. This means that the problem is not caused by another health issue. Another type of insomnia is caused by a mental health problem. There are also sleep disorders that are caused by medical problems or by using a substance.

The primary sleep disorders are called Dyssonmias or Parasomnias. Dyssonmias are problems with sleeping or staying awake. They include insomnia, hypersomnia, narcolepsy, and other sleep disorders. Insomnia is when you have trouble sleeping or staying asleep. Hypersomnia is when you have trouble staying awake. Narcolepsy is a condition that makes you fall asleep suddenly.

The sociocultural model says that insomnia can be caused by social and environmental factors. For example, a person's economic status or age can affect their sleep. Research has shown that people from different cultures and ethnic groups have different sleep patterns.

One study looked at how genetics affect sleep. The researchers used mice to study the brain's sleep centers. They found that a special type of neuron in the brain helps us sleep and wake up. They also found that a problem with this neuron can cause insomnia. This study suggests that insomnia can be caused by genetic factors.

Another study looked at how the environment affects sleep. The researchers found that people who live in noisy or stressful environments have more trouble sleeping. This study suggests that sociocultural factors can cause insomnia.

Critics of these studies say that they are too simple. They say that insomnia is caused by many different factors, and we need more research to understand it. Others say that the studies did not look at enough people, so the results may not be generalizable to the whole population.

This paper talks about Central Auditory Processing Disorder (CAPD). It covers three areas: a definition of CAPD, how to diagnose it, and how a teacher can help a student with CAPD in a classroom.

CAPD means the brain has trouble using the information we hear. The brain cannot separate sounds or understand speech well in noisy places. People with CAPD can hear normally, but their brain does not work correctly. CAPD is not the same as being deaf or hard of hearing. 

CAPD was first talked about in the 1950s. Researchers studied children who had trouble communicating. They developed special tests to help identify the problem. In 1977, a national meeting helped researchers learn more about CAPD.

People with CAPD have trouble with different things. They may not be able to find where a sound is coming from. They may have trouble hearing two or more sounds at the same time. They may not be able to recognize patterns in sounds. They may not be able to understand changes in speech. Sometimes, one sound can block out another sound. They may not be able to use sounds to make sense of things. They may not be able to tell what order sounds come in.

To find out if someone has CAPD, a doctor or a specialist uses special tests. These tests look at how the person hears and responds to sounds. There is no one test that works all the time, and we do not know what causes CAPD. Tests may ask the person to listen to many sounds at once and then say what they heard. More advanced tests measure the sounds that go into the ear and the brain's response.

A teacher in a classroom can help a student with CAPD. They can make sure the student sits near the front of the class where it is quieter. They can also ask the student to repeat what the teacher says so they can make sure they understand. The teacher can also help the student use a note-taker or a hearing aid.

The play Twelfth Night says that using a disguise can be helpful in deceiving people. But using a disguise can also cause problems. In the end, a person may have to decide between keeping their true self or keeping relationships with others. Some people may not be angry if they find out they were tricked. But others may be very upset.

The play talks about a man who dresses as a woman. This makes it a problem because it raises questions. Why does the man want to hide who he is? In the play, the man dresses as a woman to protect himself. He is in a new place and thinks it is safer. He is very good at being a man, but this makes him lose contact with his female friends. It also makes a woman fall in love with him. He also has feelings for another man.

Some people think that using a disguise can help people understand their true feelings. In the play, two people have feelings they do not express. They are able to understand these feelings when they see the man dressed as a woman. But it is not clear if these people really have feelings for the same sex or if they are just pretending.

The woman in the play is not really in love with the man. She is just pretending to be in love with him. When she meets the man who is the same as the disguised man, she falls in love with him instead. This shows that the woman does not really have feelings for the man. She is just making fun of people who judge others based on how they look.

The play is about how people can be tricked into understanding their true feelings. But it also shows that using a disguise can cause problems and make it hard for people to keep their relationships with others.

People have talked about German colonial rule being very cruel. One example is the killing of the Ovaherero and Nama people in German South West Africa. However, German colonial rule was complex and had different rules in different places. Education in the colonies was not the same. 

When the British took control of German East Africa in 1919, they found many educated and able Africans. The German government had done a good job of teaching Africans in some colonies, like Kamerun. 

But the situation in South West Africa was different. The government did not help much with the education of the native people. They mostly left it to Christian groups. The government, on the other hand, educated many German people who lived in the colony. They built schools and controlled the Christian schools. These policies had a big effect on South West Africa even after German rule ended. 

Most of the people in South West Africa did not know how to read or write. Some research says this was because of many social, economic, and political problems. This paper wants to look deeper into these problems. It also wants to look at how German settlers and colonial leaders felt about the native people.

There are many books and studies about education in the German colonies. Most of these were written in German and were published long ago. These studies mainly described how the educational systems worked in the different colonies. Later studies, written in English, compared education in the different colonies and looked at specific parts of the educational systems. One important study is by Cohen. He compared education in South West Africa and East Africa and looked at why their educational systems were different. According to Cohen, the main reason was the large number of Germans living in South West Africa.

South West Africa had a good climate, but a lot of the land was desert. Many Germans moved there because it was relatively easy to live in. By 1913, there were about 15,000 Germans living in South West Africa. This was a lot more than in East Africa, where there were about 5,300 Germans.

Heavy Metal music is a popular kind of music. It has grown over 100 years. Many people like it because it is very expressive. It shows a lot of emotions, but the emotions are often dark.

Heavy Metal music has many different kinds. Some of these kinds are very different from each other. This makes it hard to say what Heavy Metal music is. It has many ideas from other kinds of music. But Heavy Metal music started from somewhere.

Heavy Metal music is about darkness. It is often loud and has many strong beats. The people who play Heavy Metal music are very good at playing their instruments. They make the music sound very good.

Many people who play Heavy Metal music use drugs to get ideas for their music. A long time ago, there was a time when many people used drugs. This led to some strange and new kinds of music. Some of this music was very dark and scary.

Some of the ideas for Heavy Metal music came from a long time ago. This was a time when artists wrote very emotional music. Many people who play Heavy Metal music today like these old ideas.

The Beatles were one of the first groups to make Heavy Metal music. They made a song called Helter Skelter. This song is very loud and has a lot of strong beats. It is considered one of the first Heavy Metal songs. The Beatles made it to show that they could make music as loud and heavy as the Rolling Stones.

Henri Rousseau was a famous artist. He painted his dreams. His 1910 painting, The Dream, shows a woman looking at the wonders of a dreamland. It also shows Rousseau's own dreams and goals. He wanted to be famous and respected by other artists and art lovers. But he had a problem. He wanted to be accepted by the art world, but he also wanted to be creative and different.

To understand The Dream, you need to know about Rousseau's life. He was born in 1844 in a town in northwest France. His father was a tinsmith. Rousseau did not go to art school. Instead, he worked for the government until he was 40 years old. He then started painting. Painting helped him feel better after his first wife died and his children were born sick. Many artists in France painted peasants in a romantic way. But Rousseau was a folk painter. He painted what he knew from his life.

Rousseau wanted to be famous. He started painting when many other artists were already famous. He did not get recognition until many years after other famous artists like Matisse. Matisse and Rousseau were different. Matisse wanted to paint in a new and interesting way. Rousseau wanted to paint in a way that would make him accepted by the art world.

Many great thinkers have said that ethics and beauty are connected. They think that truth and beauty are the same thing. I agree with this idea. As John Keats said, "Beauty is truth. Truth is beauty. This is all you need to know." We learn many things in life through education and experience. But we appreciate beauty and morality without learning about them in school. Both ethics and beauty are about describing things, not telling us what to do. We try to explain why a piece of art or literature is beautiful, or why an action is right or wrong. But it's hard to fully understand what makes something good or beautiful.

When we talk about art, we often discuss things like how it looks or what it means. But these things don't fully explain why it's good. When someone asks about a favorite work of art, they might say, "There's something special about it." They can't fully explain what that is. I think art and morals are the same way. As Flannery O'Connor said, "A story is a way to say something that can't be said any other way." We tell stories because words alone are not enough. I think ethics is the same. As Wittgenstein said, "Ethics can't be explained. Ethics is beyond words." I think this "something special" is what makes art and morals so powerful.

I believe that ethics and art are connected because they both touch us on a deep level. We experience them in a way that can't be fully understood. This connection is especially strong with literature. Literature is special because it deals with values. As McKean said, "Literature is important to us because of the values we find there." Living involves values, and literature helps us understand those values.

Today's Germany is a strong country. It is a single country with its own culture. This culture comes from the Alps in München to the Baltic Sea city of Kiel. You can also see it in Köln on the Rhine River to the Saxon city of Dresden on the Elbe River. This unique culture comes from many different groups and tribes.

The country of Germany has a long history. We do not know for sure how it got its name. Some people think it came from a tribe called the Tungrians. They were called Germans before they moved across the Rhine River and fought against the Gauls.

The Roman leader Julius Caesar first used the word "Germanus" to describe the people he fought against. He took this word from the Gauls. The Gauls used it to describe their neighbors. Caesar wrote about the Germans in his book about the Gallic Wars. He said they lived across the Rhine River and often fought the Gauls.

Other people think the name "Germany" came from a spear called a ger. They used this spear in battle. Others think it came from an old word that means "to shout." This was because the Germans were very loud.

The Roman historian Tacitus wrote about the Germans in the year 98 AD. He said they were an old group of people who did not mix with other groups. He said they were a difficult group to visit because of their rough land and weather. He also said they had a hard time being friends with the Romans.

The Germanic tribes lived on the borders of the Roman Empire. They traded goods and skills with the Romans. They also served in the Roman army. This helped them learn from the Romans and improve their own country.

I stared down at the bowl in front of me. My mind was empty and quiet. I was looking at a picture, but I did not think about it much. My mind was like a calm lake. It was looking at the picture, but it was not thinking about it.

I had a book on art once. It was called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain." An artist I worked with told me about it. I wanted to learn to draw when I was six years old. The book teaches how to draw. It says to put a frame around the picture you want to draw. This helps you see it more clearly.

I was looking at a bowl of fruit on a table. But I was too busy to think about drawing it. I was amazed by the picture. It was too much for me to handle. The artist Picasso liked blue. Monet liked green. Old Italian artists used many colors. If I wanted to be an artist, this picture could be my start.

I picked up a pencil. My hand moved over the paper. I wanted to draw. But my hand was not listening to me. It went to the toilet instead. I tried to draw, but my hand hit the toilet handle. The brown package in the toilet bowl did not move. It was stuck.

I used a mop to clean the toilet. I put on my green tie and frowned. I looked at the package. It was a mess. It was someone else's problem. I wanted some peace and quiet. I held the toilet paper roll and wrapped it around my hand like a mitt. I bent down and put my hand in the water. It was like putting a turkey in the oven.

Many young drivers are dying in car accidents.  Several things come together to cause this problem.  One thing is that young brains are not ready for driving.  They do not have enough experience.  This lack of experience causes many more accidents, and also more accidents where cars turn over, speed, or go off the road.

Young people also drive more carefully when they are with older drivers.  This is true  A study in Southern California found that the age of the passenger affects the number of car accidents.

Some states have a special license for young drivers.  This license limits the hours they can drive and the number of people they can have in the car.  But this is not enough to solve the problem.  The problem is that young drivers are not ready to handle the risks of driving.  A scientist named Marvin Zuckerman thinks that 18 is too young to get a driver's license.  He says that people under 19 or 20 often like to take risks just for the fun of it.  This is why we should wait until they are older to let them drive.

If we continue to give licenses to young drivers, we will see more accidents and more people will die.  In a few years, many more young drivers will be on the road.  This could be very bad.

We can solve this problem with a new law.  Schools can teach people to drive, but no one under 18 can get a driver's license.  A young person can still get a permit before they get a full license.  They will still have to practice driving with an adult for a certain number of hours.  The number of hours can be the same as most states now require.  A national law would be a good way to keep young drivers safe across the country.

This idea is not new.  Other people have thought of it before.

I looked at movies from the Library of Congress. They are from the early days of film maker Thomas Edison. I wanted to see all the movies that used tricks. There were fifteen of these movies from 1895 to 1901. These films use creative editing to make tricks. My study of film looked at how most of these movies used tricks. I also looked at some later movies that did things differently. At the time, trick movies usually take place on a stage. The camera does not move. It shows the whole scene at once. The movies use many long shots and some medium shots. But they do not use close-up shots.

Many of these movies are set on a stage with a front wall. The camera does not move to follow actors. It stays in one place. This style came from the theater and magic shows. Actors in these movies can only move side to side. They do not walk towards or away from the camera. For example, in the movie Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel (1900), the actors come in from the right and move back and forth.

Most of these movies also use long shots and some medium shots. Close-up shots are never used. This is because the theater and magic shows show the whole performance at once. The audience sees the whole scene, not just a small part. Most of these movies are short, about one minute or less. They show simple tricks like magic and disappearing acts. But sometimes, one "shot" in the movie can be made from many physical shots. Look at The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots (1895) and you will see how it is done.

John Taylor was a big supporter of the idea of being a republic. He was a farmer and a politician. Because of these jobs, he was known for his strong feelings about freedom and government. He believed that farming was the best job. This idea influenced his thoughts about government, the law, and the court system.

John Taylor thought the United States had a great chance to make a perfect system of government. This was because there was no tradition from the past to follow. He believed in the idea that people have natural rights. These rights are important because they are all connected. If one right is taken away, the other rights are not as valuable. He thought the government should not control these rights. He believed that in a natural state, strong people would take advantage of others. But in a society, this should not happen.

To create a perfect society, Taylor thought the government should understand that people have good and bad qualities. He believed in a simple way of thinking about good and bad. He said that governments are run by people and have good and bad qualities. He thought a good government should protect private property, help farming, and not support a system where some people get rich at the expense of others. He believed that a good government would work well, even if its leaders are selfish. He thought selfishness is a natural part of people, but it is bad when it hurts others. A good government should keep people from being too selfish.

Taylor, like many other Republicans, wanted the government to follow the Constitution closely. He wanted the government to have only the powers that the Constitution said it could have. He thought a big government was expensive and might be cruel. But he also thought that following the Constitution too closely could be bad. He believed that the Declaration of Independence was a more important document than the Constitution. This is because it said that the United States was made up of many independent states, not just one country.

We look at Figure 17. There was a big drop in commuter log submissions in the third month. We do not know why this happened. It was winter in New England, so fewer people rode bicycles or walked. This might be part of the reason for the drop. The end of the fall semester was also in December. Students were busy with schoolwork and grades. They might have forgotten to fill out the log. Many students and teachers do not come to campus in December because of the holiday season. They do not need to come to campus during the long break. Classes started again in late January. This might also be a reason for the low number of submissions. But this still does not explain the low number of submissions in February. Maybe a project like this starts with a lot of energy, but then the energy goes down. We tried to fix this with the Carpool Challenge Week in March. This was a special week to make people think about the project again. It worked and we got more log submissions. So, one of our problems was keeping the project going. We had a natural decrease in interest, but also a problem with the breaks at school. 

Another problem with this project is that many people like driving their cars. This is a part of our culture. We need to give people reasons to use other ways to get to campus. We gave prizes to people who used alternative transportation. These prizes were gift certificates to local stores. It would have been interesting to see how bigger prizes might have worked. For example, giving away a bicycle or a car might have made more people participate. The prizes did not change during the project. If we had made the prizes bigger as the project went on, that might have helped. The first prizes were good, but if we had offered more prizes in December and January, like a bicycle or a car, more people might have participated.

An ETF, or exchange traded fund, is a security that tracks an index, a commodity, or a group of assets. It is like an index fund but more flexible and trades like a stock on an exchange. An ETF gives you the benefits of an index fund and the freedom to sell short, buy on margin, and buy one share at a time. ETFs have low expense ratios, lower than the average mutual fund. But, you must pay a commission for each trade, like buying a stock. Many ETFs are available, giving you choices. However, it is smart to check if the benefits, like diversification, really exist and to what extent.

We are studying the ETF IHF and comparing it to the top 10 stocks that make up 63.58% of its assets. We will see if owning a single ETF is as good as owning a group of the 10 stocks. We will also see if there is a better way to combine these stocks for higher returns.

To make it easy, we are only looking at the top 10 stocks. Here are the stocks and their percentage of the total assets.

To see how well these 10 stocks represent the ETF IHF, we will calculate their Beta and Return. We will use the current percentages to make a chart.

The chart shows that the 10 stocks have a 6.11% higher return than the ETF. The Beta of the 10 stocks is 0.12 lower than the ETF. This means a portfolio of just the top 10 holdings could have a higher return with less risk. But, there is a chance the difference is not real.

To be sure, we need to compare the standard deviation of each stock and the ETF. We will make a chart to see if the differences are real.

One of Edgar Allan Poe's good poems is "Dream-Land". In "Dream-Land", Poe uses the word "Thulé" two times. The word "Thulé" comes from the Roman writer Virgil. Virgil used "Thulé" in his writing to describe an island north of Britain. The Greeks thought this island was the edge of the world.

Poe read many German books. One German writer he liked was Goethe. Goethe wrote a play called "Faust". It was first published in 1808 and the second part was published in 1832, the year Goethe died. Inside "Faust", there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé". The poem is about a king whose wife dies after giving him a special cup. After she dies, the king drinks a lot and cries about his dead wife. He decides it is time to die and gives his things to his children. He then throws the cup into the ocean, closes his eyes, and dies.

The king in "The King of Thulé" and the king in "Dream-Land" are similar. Maybe Poe used the idea of the king in "The King of Thulé" as a way to say how much he missed his own loved ones. Goethe's play "Faust" was also made into a play by H P Grattan in 1842, one year before Poe used the word "Thule" in his poem "The Pit and the Pendulum".

Poe used the word "Thulé" in two of his writings. One time he wrote "ultma Thule" in "The Pit and the Pendulum". But in "Dream-Land", he used "Thulé" at the beginning and the end of the poem. "The King of Thulé" and "Dream-Land" can be read together as two connected poems. In "Dream-Land", the speaker talks about a land that is dark, lonely, and full of death. He also sees a world without colors. All of these things can be compared to "The King of Thulé" where the king is lonely and sad after his wife dies.

Goethe was a famous writer that Poe would have known because he liked another writer, Tennyson. Poe said he liked Tennyson. Poe would have also read Goethe's books because many of his books were published in many countries after the first one came out.

In California, if a customer gets hurt after slipping and falling on an applesauce spill in a store, can they get extra money because the store manager acted very badly? The store manager, Paul Martin, was told twice about the spill, but he did not clean it up for 30 minutes because he was eating dinner.

A judge is unlikely to quickly reject a customer's request for extra money. To get extra money, the customer must show that the store manager acted very badly on purpose, and that he did not care about the harm this would cause. The customer can argue that the store manager should have known that not cleaning the spill was very bad because many people had slipped on spills in the store before. The customer can also argue that the store manager did not take care of the problem even though he knew it was a problem.

The customer's argument that the store manager acted very badly is not very strong, but it is still reasonable. This is because there were six slip-and-fall accidents in the store in 2009, and the manager did not do anything to make the store safe.

On October 13, 2009, a worker at the store told the manager about the applesauce spill. The manager said he was on break and did not have time to deal with customers. Later, another worker told the manager about the spill again, and he said the same thing. At 5:30 pm, the customer slipped and fell on the spill and got hurt badly. Before this, there had been five other slip-and-fall accidents in the store in 2009.

The customer is now suing the store for money because of her injury. We are looking at whether to ask the judge to quickly decide if the customer should get extra money because of the store manager's bad behavior.

In California, a customer can get extra money if the store acted very badly and broke a rule. The rule says that the store must not act with "oppression, fraud, or malice." Malice means that the store acted on purpose to hurt someone, or if it did not act on purpose, it acted very badly and did not care about the harm it would cause. Courts have said that a store acts very badly if it knows that its actions will cause harm, but it still does its actions anyway.

I took a class in Islam at CBC about four years ago.  We discussed if Islam is a hostile religion.  I think this question is more important now than ever.  Since 9/11, I have noticed that media in America has changed from being against Islam to very tolerant.  I don't think a president with Muslim background like Barack Obama would have been elected in 2001.

The life of Muhammad is interesting to me.  What I know about his history does not match my idea of him.  I thought Muhammad forced people to become Muslim.  He would conquer tribes and make them join Islam.  But his biography says he was a kind and humble man.  People came to him because they believed in his teachings.

There are some special things about Muhammad's life that are like Jesus'.  One example is when he had little food and made it enough for many people.  This makes me think the writers wanted to show Muhammad as a kind prophet who didn't need to prove anything.  This doesn't seem right because it takes away from Jesus' life and teachings.

There are many stories in the biography that seem to be trying to show how people became Muslim on their own.  But these stories are often from people who heard from others.  This makes the stories seem less believable.

What bothers me most is that the writers try to show Muhammad as a kind and wise man.  But history says something different.  I wonder if Muslims know the real story of Muhammad's life.

The teachings of Jesus and his beliefs were left behind when Christianity developed after his death.  If we look at the history of Christianity, we see a trend.  It moves away from its roots.  Today, there is a growing awareness and a desire for change.  Traditional people will hold on to what they were taught.  But they are not the majority.  In the future, people will understand the real meaning of Christianity.  They will separate the old ideas added to the religion from Jesus' true message.  This will take time, maybe many years or even centuries.  But it will happen.  The trend of Christian history will change.  People will go back to what Jesus taught.  A movement will grow.  It will remove the old ideas one by one.  The result will be a return to Jesus' ideas, not the ideas of later thinkers.  When this happens in the United States and Europe, many people will follow Jesus' teachings.  They will follow only his ideas.  The church will still be strong and lead the way.  But the many different ideas in Christianity will become fewer.  There will be more agreement about what to believe and how to act.  The world has seen great changes before.  For example, Christians were once persecuted by the Roman Empire.  But later, the empire became Christian.  Our country has changed from slavery to freedom.  A great change is coming.  It will happen in the Christian world.  We will look back to the source of the Christian religion.  We will search for the truth.  This will make it possible to read Jesus' words as symbols, not as literal statements.  What happened after Jesus' death?

Looking far back in history, we find only Judaism.  It is the beginning of the Christian religion.  Judaism believed in one God, and the authority of the Hebrew scriptures.  These were the core ideas of the religion when the Romans took control of Jerusalem in 63 B.C.  The Jewish people were not all the same.  They divided into different groups, like the Sadducees, Pharisees, Essenes, Zealots, and the common people.

I think The Jungle shows that people are naturally selfish. They only think about themselves and try to make their lives better. They do not care about others who are less successful than them. The book shows this in many ways. The owners of big factories only want to make their companies bigger and wealthier. They do not care about anything that gets in their way or anything that gets hurt because of their work. They do not think about the pollution they create or the animals that suffer because of it. 

The owners also do not care about their workers. They make their workers work very long hours and do not give them any help when they need it. If they want to save money, they will fire many workers at the same time without warning. There were no laws to protect workers in that time, so the owners could do as they wanted. The people who worked and lived in Packingtown were expected to live in very bad conditions. There were no organizations to help them. Some groups, called unions, were formed, but they often helped the owners instead of the workers. The workers were very unhappy and had no way to escape the problems of Packingtown. They were treated like slaves.

The Jungle says that people in these conditions will act very badly. They will do things that are not right just to survive. This is like slavery.

F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many ways to make readers feel a certain way about important things. He uses these ways to make readers feel good or bad about things. Sometimes, Fitzgerald pairs words that do not usually go together to make a special feeling around a subject. Other times, he gives a special meaning to a picture and uses it to make the same feeling. Fitzgerald does this with many colors, including gold, green, white, gray, red, and pink. In his book The Great Gatsby, Fitzgerald makes a special meaning for white and gray colors. He then uses that meaning to make readers have a certain feeling about an important object.

Fitzgerald makes the meaning for white and gray to be about being the same. White is a little better and more important. Gray is older and not as new. Fitzgerald starts this in the beginning of the book. He uses these colors a lot. For example, Daisy and Jordan are always wearing white. Nick wears white clothes to Gatsby's party. Tom wears a white shirt to meet Myrtle. Catherine is very white. The only time people are not wearing white is when Nick is getting a picture of Gatsby's party. The place is colorful. Fitzgerald makes these colors more clear by using them to describe small things. For example, he describes Nick going down a long white area of New York. Gray names are on Nick's list. Catherine's apartment is in a long row of white houses. He also describes plain people or places as white or gray. Jordan and Daisy had a happy white childhood together. There are gray cars and gray land in a place that is not good. A man selling dogs is gray.

After Fitzgerald makes the meaning clear, he uses these colors to show that something is not important or is the same. This starts with Daisy. Fitzgerald does not use these colors for a long time. Then he describes Daisy as wearing white in a white car. Readers start to see Daisy as not special, just something that Gatsby wants. Fitzgerald uses this technique again around Daisy to make her seem not special. For example, there is a gray collar on Daisy's coat. She is in a white dress before Tom and Gatsby meet.

San Diego County has a good climate for farming. Many crops grow well there. These include tomatoes, citrus fruits, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, herbs, and fruits like peaches and lemons. Berries and honey are also grown there. People in San Diego want to buy food from local farms. Many of these farms are organic. This means they do not use chemicals. They have waiting lists of people who want to buy their food.

Organic farms in the area also offer tours. People can walk or hike on the land. They can see birds and other animals. Some farms have special programs. These programs teach people about farming and how to take care of the land.

Organic farming is good for the environment. It helps keep the soil and water clean. This makes a healthy home for plants and animals. However, organic farming is more expensive than regular farming. It takes more workers to take care of the land without using chemicals. The farmers may lose more crops than regular farmers. Organic farms are often small. They do not have the same efficiency as big farms.

The land I am talking about is in San Diego County, California. It is 160 acres of land. This land is next to a forest and has many different types of plants and animals. Some of these animals are in danger. They include the Stephens' kangaroo rat, the mountain yellow-legged frog, and several kinds of butterflies. The land was once home to Native Americans. Later, people raised cattle and cut wood there.

I found a real farm in the same area. It is an organic farm. I studied government programs that help small farmers. These programs can make farming easier and cheaper. They can also help farmers take care of the land and the animals that live there.

Culture is very important in negotiation. To understand culture, we must know what it is not. Culture is not the same everywhere. It is not one thing or the same for everyone. People often make general statements about a country or group, like "all Russians are stubborn." But these statements are not true.

It is better to understand how a culture feels about a situation. We can learn about a culture by studying its history, its customs, and its values. We should not try to change a culture or judge it. We should accept it and work with it. This is especially important when we are in a weak position in a negotiation. Showing respect for a culture can help us get past any problems and move forward.

Culture is not just about countries or nations. Companies also have their own cultures. For example, some companies work very long hours, while others have more relaxed schedules. We can see a company's culture in how its employees dress, how they communicate, and how they work together. Some companies want their employees to be involved in charity work, while others do not.

Understanding values is very important too. Values are the reasons behind a culture. For example, if a culture values being polite, someone from that culture will not want to make their company or boss look bad in public. If a culture values making a good deal, someone from that culture will not give up easily. We should think about these things before we start negotiating. We should also try to get to know the person we are negotiating with, so we can make the negotiation more effective.

A famous Bible quote says, "The fool says in his heart, 'There is no God.'" This quote is from Psalm 14. It is also the start of a discussion by St. Anselm about the existence of God. Thomas Aquinas also believes in God. Both have good reasons to believe. To compare their ideas, we must first assume they are both right about the God of the Bible. If we had a different idea of God, we could not compare their ideas. 

We will look at both men's ideas. St. Anselm says we can find God inside ourselves. He says we cannot think of a God that does not exist. This idea is hard to explain. But in simple words, it means the proof of God is in our minds. Anselm says we do not need outside evidence to prove God exists. This idea is called faith. Faith is trusting in something without proof.

Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He says we can prove God exists with reason and evidence. We do not need faith. This idea is good for spreading the message of God. We can use logic to convince people to believe. Aquinas gives five reasons to prove God exists. These are change, cause, chance, good and bad things, and order. He says we can know God is real by using these reasons.

A long time ago, in the fifth or sixth century BCE, a prince was born. He would later be called Buddha. He gave up the world and became wise. His teachings created Buddhism. One part of Buddhism is called Theravada Buddhism. This religion is about 2,500 years old. It has changed over time. You can see this in the Theravada country of Sri Lanka. There, people celebrate a special ceremony every year. Monks and lay people take part in this ceremony. But Buddha never taught about this festival. These changes are not just in small things. They also affect the main ideas of the religion.

We need to understand some special terms. We will use them often. An internal force is a force from within the Buddhist group. An external force is a force from someone who is not Buddhist. A hostile force is any force that hurts the Buddhist group. A benign force is a force that does not want to hurt the Buddhist group, but may still cause harm.

First, let's look at the main ideas of Theravada Buddhism. Buddhists trust in three things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is a collection of Buddhist texts. It has three parts: the Sutta Pitaka, the Vinaya Pitaka, and the Abhidhamma Pitaka. The Sutta Pitaka has the teachings of the Buddha. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for living. The Abhidhamma Pitaka has ideas about the nature of things. Some of these ideas are Anatta (there is no soul), Dukkha (life is suffering), and Anicca (everything is impermanent). If we understand these ideas, we can end Sansara, the cycle of death and rebirth. We can also end lobha (desire), dosa (hatred), and moha (delusion). This happens when we become enlightened. The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for how to live. Lay people have five rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not be immoral, and do not take drugs. Monks have many more rules. The most important idea in Buddhism is the four noble truths. First, life is suffering. Second, attachment causes suffering. Third, suffering can be overcome.

The United States and Mexico had a long time rivalry.  It lasted 57 years, from 1836 to 1893. (Diehl and Goerts 2000, p. 145) The biggest fight was the Mexican-American War of 1846-1848. The United States won and took Texas and the Southwest from Mexico. There were many other fights. The rivalry stopped just before World War I. 

This is not new. Many countries have a long time rivalry with a neighbor.  Countries that share a border often have disagreements. These disagreements can make two countries enemies. The United States and Mexico are like many other countries that have a long time rivalry. David M. Pletcher (1977) says that there are only two countries in the world with a long time rivalry with the United States. One is Mexico and the other is Cuba. Both countries are close to the United States. They have been enemies of the United States for a long time. Other countries in Latin America have good relations with the United States.

Religion was a problem between the United States and Mexico. This is not new. Many countries have had problems because of religion in the past. Sally Frahm (2001) says that Americans did not like Catholicism and monarchy in the 18th and 19th centuries. This was a big problem between the United States and Mexico. The two countries did not like each other because of their different beliefs.

The United States and Mexico did not like each other because they inherited feelings of distrust from their former rulers. The English and Spanish did not like each other, and this feeling was passed down to the United States and Mexico. This made it difficult for the two countries to have good relations.

Diehl and Goerts (2000) say that there were 17 fights between the United States and Mexico during their 57-year rivalry. Most of the fights were about border problems and raids from Mexico into the United States. The problem of border raids went on for a long time. It stopped only when both countries used their military to control their borders. 

Schmitt (1974) says that the rivalry ended as Mexico became dependent on the United States. The United States changed its goals from taking land to helping Mexico economically. This happened in the late 19th century.

Fifteen years ago, I became very sick with an illness I did not know I had. I was a nurse at that time. I chose my job because I wanted to be safe and have a good life. When I was young, people told me, "You will always have a job. People will always get sick."

I wanted to be a scientist or a journalist, but I chose nursing instead. Now, I am 46 years old and alone. I have no money and cannot work. I get help from Social Security, but every day is hard. I feel afraid and sad.

I have been dependent on my family and some friends for support. I know that without them, I would not have made it. When bad things happen, it is hard to be strong.

My point is that everyone has bad times. We cannot always be alone and handle everything on our own. We need help and support from others.

I think the United States government is not always reliable. It is like a broken house. We should learn to trust and help each other instead of just relying on the government.

The people who started this country were not alone. They had each other's help and support. We, too, can learn from that.

I am prepared for emergencies. I have a special box with food, water, and other things I need. I have flashlights and candles, too. But being prepared is not the only thing. We need to know our neighbors and help each other.

Why do living things change over time? Are there limits to how they change? Many people have tried to answer these questions, but it is still not easy. In 1917, a scientist named D'Arcy Thompson said that it is hard to explain even simple living things in simple terms. Today, we use math to study how living things change. We are also using math to study how a group of animals called mollusks grow their shells. Our study is looking at how math and experiments can help us understand how living things change over time.

We studied a group of mollusks called Prunum. We used special pictures of their shells to find numbers that we can use in math problems. We used a computer program to make math models of their shells. These models can help us understand how their shells can change. We combined our math models with experiments and observations to learn more about how these animals change over time.

A shell is like a tube that grows as the animal gets older. It grows in a spiral shape around a central point. We can count the turns of the spiral, which are called whorls. Each whorl has a line that separates it from the one before it. This line is called a suture. The biggest whorl is the one at the end of the shell. The tip of the shell is called the apex, and the other end is called the base. The animal comes out of its shell through an opening called the aperture.

We can look at shells from different angles. One way is to look at the tip, another way is to look at the base, and another way is to look at the opening. Most people look at shells from the side, with the opening facing them.

To count the whorls, we look at the shell from the tip. We draw a line where the first suture starts. Then we count the whorls from that line. We can estimate the number of whorls to a quarter of one.

A shell is like a path that the animal follows as it grows. We can find the path by looking at the center of each whorl and the size of the opening. We can draw a picture of the path and write math equations to explain it. Once we have a math equation, we can change the numbers and see how the shell changes.

Indonesia has not seen much change in the death rate of newborn and baby children over the last 10 years.  The country is on track to meet some of the goals set by the Millennium Development Plans, like improving water and sanitation.  However, the country is not meeting its goals for improving the health of children and mothers.  The country needs to improve its health system, not just individual health programs.

Indonesia has made some progress.  More babies are now born with a trained health worker present.  But this does not mean that the health worker is a doctor.  Many are nurses or midwives who cannot help if there are serious problems.  This means many mothers die from bleeding during pregnancy.  Indonesia needs to do more to improve this area.  Fewer children under five years old are being treated for diarrhea.  We do not have complete information about how well new mothers are being taken care of after giving birth.  But it is clear that this is a problem.

More babies are not born by C-section than they should be.  There is a problem with how babies are born in rural areas.  In cities, 7% of babies are born by C-section.  In rural areas, it is only 2%.  This shows that people in cities have better access to healthcare.  Another problem is that the rich have better access to healthcare than the poor.  The poor have to pay money out of their own pockets, and this makes it hard for them to get the care they need.

The next step is to find a way to make healthcare services more available.  One question is whether Indonesia should focus on one area at a time or improve the overall healthcare system.  Program-specific approaches can be effective and fast.  But they have some problems.  Investing in one area can mean less money for other important areas.  This can cause problems with training and equipment.  It can also cause confusion and waste.

Victorian novels are known for their detailed descriptions. But two novels, Oliver Twist and Wuthering Heights, are different from others in this group. They use mystery and strange events to make their characters more interesting. These unusual events give us a better understanding of the characters' feelings and reasons for acting in certain ways.

For example, in Oliver Twist, the main character has many strange thoughts and feelings. He is walking with two men who are arguing. The words they are saying are loud in his ears. He looks around and sees that there is a lot of noise and confusion. He is being taken away quickly, but he feels a lot of pain.

In these novels, the authors use strange and unclear events to show what is happening inside the characters' minds. In Oliver Twist, these events often help us understand what is hurting Oliver and what he knows about the world around him. In one scene, Oliver relives a shooting that happened earlier in the book. He sees and feels it as if it is happening again. This scene shows that Oliver has no control over the events in his life. He is in a lot of pain and is afraid.

Oliver's lack of control is clear when he cannot even try to stop what is happening to him, even when his life is in danger. This makes us think that Oliver is giving up. He may be losing his ability to make choices and act on his own. Otherwise, he would try to save himself, even if it was just for his own life.

Another example from Wuthering Heights is: "The day passed quickly – but it was not a real day. It was gone before it started, and the night came back again. The night was long and quiet – but it was also short. It lasted only a few hours."

I worked with a program for students after school two years ago. My job was to help them with their school work. I was good at helping with English and reading. A teacher asked me to work with a boy named Adrian. He was having trouble reading. I was surprised. He could speak English well, but he had trouble with the letters. Some letters he knew, but others he did not.

I thought he might have a problem because his family was from a different country. When his mother came to talk to me, I could not understand her. She only spoke Spanish. But we were able to talk a little bit. I then understood the problem. Adrian knew how to read, but he did not know the English alphabet.

I tell this story to show that language can be a big problem for some students. Even if a student speaks English well, reading can still be hard. I think many people agree that this is a big problem. So, what can we do? I think tutoring in reading, especially the alphabet and how to say the letters, can help. But for students who do not speak English well, it is harder.

There is no one solution to the problem. Some people think that bilingual programs are good. This means teaching students two languages at the same time. Research shows that students in these programs do well in school. Some people are afraid that it will not help many students. They think it is a waste of time and money. But this is not true. If we make bilingual programs the rule, not the exception, all students will benefit.

So, how do we do this? Do we make all teachers speak two languages? No, that is not possible or fair. But we can have special helpers, like tutors, who speak two languages. They can work with students who need help.

We are taught from a young age that something big is out there that we cannot understand.  Some people go to school to learn about it.  Others search within themselves for answers.  Many people accept the religions taught by their parents.  But some people do not believe.  They think there is no life after death.  We look for a way to understand the world.  We search for a light in the dark.

One day, my father and I sat on our porch.  We listened to the rain.  He said, "A cardinal is my favorite bird."  I asked him why.  He looked out into the rain.  His eyes looked sad.  He was not eating well and looked weak.  I sat close to him.  We watched the rain together.

Later, my father died.  He was sick for a long time.  The medicine did not help.  He lived a few more months than the doctors said.  I was sad.  I thought, "What kind of God would make him suffer?"  I did not pray.  If God existed, I thought, he was not listening to me.

I did not want to see my father die.  I wanted to remember how he lived, not how he died.  I knew my father better than anyone else.  I knew he would not want me to see him die.  I stayed in my bed for three days.  I waited for news.  But no one called me.

The Gothic novel is a mix of old and new ideas. It is also called an oxymoron, which means a combination of two things that do not go together, like 'old' and 'new.' 

The first Gothic novel was written by Horace Walpole. It is called "The Castle of Otranto." Walpole used old and new ideas to create a new kind of story. He took old theatrical elements and combined them with new ideas from modern novels. This created a new way of writing.

The Gothic novel is based on old things like medieval theater, architecture, and traditions. Many people thought these old things were old-fashioned and not good enough for modern times. But Walpole used these old things in a new way to create a new kind of story.

One important idea in Gothic novels is chivalry. Chivalry is a quality that knights are supposed to have. They are brave, honest, and kind. Walpole wanted to show that people in his time did not have these qualities. He wrote about a character named Frederic. Frederic is a prince who is brave and kind. He has suffered a lot and is supposed to be dead. But he is not. He is a good example of a knight.

Walpole wrote "The Castle of Otranto" during a time when there was a lot of trouble in the country. He was unhappy with the way things were going. He wanted to write about a time when things were better. He used the idea of chivalry to show that people in his time were not living up to the standards of the past. He wanted to say that people were not as good as they used to be.

Walpole's ideas about chivalry and the past are still popular today. They are part of the Gothic style of writing, which is still used in many stories. The Gothic novel is a mix of old and new ideas, and it continues to be popular because of its unique style.

The supply chain is a series of steps to get goods from the customer to the customer. It starts with the raw materials and ends with the customer.  This idea was first used in 1982 by a man named Keith Oliver.  Keith Oliver said that supply chain management is planning, making decisions, and controlling the process to meet customers' needs quickly and efficiently. 

There are six main parts of a supply chain: production, supply, inventory, location, transportation, and information. Business managers use these parts to give good service to their customers.

Production is the first step. Production is the foundation for the whole supply chain. It decides when, why, where, and how things are made. Managers must know what customers want. They look at the market to find out what the customers want. The market is the biggest sign of what customers want. After looking at the market, managers decide what products to make and how many to make. They also decide where to make the products and what plant will be best for quality and amount. They think about customer demand and satisfaction. After choosing a place to make the products, managers focus on planning workloads and equipment maintenance.

Supply is the second key part. Supply means making decisions about what a business can do best and what to do with others. A business can have many teams to make a product. Each team has different tools, workers, and experts. Managers decide which team is best for each step. They may also send work to other companies. The main reason is to go faster and be flexible while keeping costs low.

These two parts are very important. If they are not planned carefully, a company may lose time and money in the long run. For example, I worked at Wal-Mart and Target. They have a plan for every part of the business. They have a design for employee uniforms and a plan for when shipments come in. This helps the company work smoothly and avoid confusion.

Other key parts of the supply chain are inventory, location, transportation, and information. Managers use these parts to give good service to customers.

A sign in Burma, also known as Myanmar, says Hitler is still alive. Ellen Page, a famous actress, stands alone on a street corner with a piece of cardboard. The sign on the cardboard is very disturbing.

Burma is a country in Southeast Asia. A group of military leaders took control of the country in 1962. In 2007, many people went to the streets to protest against the government. They were led by Buddhist monks, who wear orange robes. The protests were called the Saffron Revolution. But the military leaders did not like the protests. They started to be violent. They even attacked and destroyed some of the monks' homes.

Foreign journalists, people who report news, were arrested. A Japanese journalist was killed while he was reporting on a protest. The government said 13 people died, but a former army leader said that many more people were killed. He said that it is hard to count the number of deaths because the bodies are hidden.

This is not a new problem. Governments have been trying to control their people for a long time. Even in ancient times, leaders claimed they were chosen by gods to rule. In some countries, leaders are still believed to be gods. In the United States, the president talks to a leader of a church group.

There have been many examples of governments being very strict and controlling. In 1989, many students and activists protested in China. The Chinese government said that 200-300 people died, but others said that 2,000-3,000 people died. In Rwanda, a group of people killed many others because of their ethnic group. In Germany, a leader named Hitler and his followers killed many Jewish people.

Duke Ellington was a famous jazz musician. He made jazz better because he lived a long time and was very good at creating music. Often, Ellington played the piano in his songs, but he was also very good at writing music for his whole band. He made a framework for band members to play their own music. Ellington also wrote music that each band member could play in their own special way. This made his music sound good and original.

The Grove Music dictionary says Ellington was good at using voice like a musical instrument in his songs. This was true from the beginning of his career. A good example is Creole Love Call. This slow song is a blues piece with six parts. Each part is different and has a special sound.

Part 1: The voice and woodwind instruments talk to each other. The voice starts singing smooth and then gets rough.
Part 2: A trumpet player sings a solo. He plays high notes and adds to the song.
Part 3: A clarinet player plays a fast, high solo. The piano player adds a special rhythm to the music.
Part 4: The whole band sings like the first part. The brass and woodwind instruments talk to each other.
Part 5: This is the most exciting part of the song. The woodwind instruments start singing, and the brass and rhythm players add a special sound.
Part 6: The song goes back to the first part, but the voice sounds like it is growling. The voice plays like a musical instrument.

Ellington used voice to add color to his music. This is one reason his songs are special.

In another song, Hot and Bothered, Ellington uses his skill at writing music for his band. He also uses his ear to make the music sound good. The song has a special sound because of the way the trumpet and voice play together.

In another song, It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing), Ellington uses a trombone player named Joe Nanton. Nanton is very good at playing the trombone, and Ellington uses him to start the song.

Ellington was a great musician because he was good at using voice and instruments to make music that sounds good. His songs are still popular today.

She had a big need. It was a feeling that she could not stop. It started when she was 14. She was growing up and trying to be a young adult. Three years later, at 17, it was still there. She decided she wanted a person, not just something. But she did not feel attracted to any boys. Some boys liked her, but she did not like them. She asked herself many times, "Why is this happening to me?" She thought about many reasons, but she did not think it was a good idea.

Most days at home were calm. Her parents were good people. They never argued with each other. They rarely argued with her too. They argued about her wanting to be independent and free. She liked to be different and energetic. This made her a nice person that people liked.

Today was not a calm day. She was looking for something new to be excited about. She heard a loud cry from the kitchen. It was her mother's voice. She ran to the kitchen. She saw her mother on the ground. Her mother was hurt. She was saying "Ow" in short breaths. She put her hand on her mother to help. "Ouch ... sweetie, I need you to take me to the hospital." Her mother was in a lot of pain. "Okay Mom, where can I pick you up?" Her mother showed her with her hands. She was happy she could help her mother because of some classes she took to be strong. She carried her mother to the car and put her in the back. Then she drove to the hospital.

The hospital had a strong smell of sickness. She was not scared. She was worried about her mother. She helped her mother lie down on a special bed. Then she called for the doctors to help. Some doctors came and took her mother to be looked at. Her daughter waited in worry.

Her mother fell off a small step stool. She was trying to get a vase from a high cabinet.

This study looked at how following a "Mediterranean Diet" can lower the risk of heart disease and stroke. The study used a "Mediterranean Diet Score" to measure how well people followed the diet. A high score means people ate a lot of plant food, like fruits, nuts, and whole grains. They ate less animal food and fat. A little bit of alcohol was okay.

Past studies showed that following the Mediterranean Diet can lower the risk of heart disease and death from heart disease. But these studies did not look at stroke. This study looked at 74,886 women who were 38 to 63 years old and did not have heart disease or diabetes. They were part of a big study of female nurses.

The researchers used food questionnaires to see what the women ate. They asked the women what they ate every year for 20 years. Most of the women answered the questionnaires all 20 years. The researchers checked the food questionnaires against medical records to see if the women got heart disease or had a stroke. They also checked if the women smoked, were overweight, or took aspirin.

To get a better idea of what the women ate over time, the researchers averaged the food questionnaires from two years at a time. They then adjusted the results to remove things that could make the results seem different, like age, smoking, and weight.

The researchers used a special method to see if the Mediterranean Diet lowered the risk of heart disease and stroke. They found that women who ate a lot of plant food and less animal food had a lower risk of heart disease and stroke. After 20 years, 2391 women got heart disease, 1763 got a stroke, and 1077 died from heart disease or a stroke. Women who ate a lot of plant food had a 29% lower risk of heart disease and a 29% lower risk of stroke.

In 2007, America had a big economic problem. Many people lost their jobs. The housing market crashed. Many big companies went out of business. This economic problem is still here today. We need to know how this problem started and how to stop it. The problem started because of bad decisions made by some people in government. They wanted banks to give loans to people who could not pay them back. The banks also sold these bad loans to other companies. This caused a big problem when people could not pay their loans.

The problem started 12 years earlier. President Clinton wanted to be re-elected. He wanted to be popular. So, he changed the rules to make it easier to get loans. This made it easier for people to get loans they could not pay back. A reporter in the New York Times wrote about this in 1999. He said the government was pressuring a company called Fannie Mae to give loans to people who could not pay them back. He said this could cause big problems in the future.

The housing market was also very complicated. Banks were giving out loans that people could not pay back. They were selling these loans to other companies. This connected many parts of the economy to the housing market. Many people in America were borrowing too much money. When the housing market crashed, these people could not pay their loans. The companies that sold these bad loans had big problems.

In 2007, the top five big banks in America had $4.1 trillion dollars of bad loans. This was 30% of America's total economy. The government had to help some of these banks. The company Fannie Mae had $5 trillion dollars of bad loans. The government had to control it in 2008.

Exposition is a part of a story where the writer tells the reader information about the characters and setting. But sometimes, too much exposition can be bad. It is like a long, boring speech that makes the reader want to fall asleep.

Dr. Merlin is a writer who knows about this problem. She calls it "Too Much Information." She says it is like having a devil on the shoulder that tells you to tell too much about the story.

Exposition is when the writer tells the reader what happened. It is like a character in a movie saying, "I'll tell you the whole story." In a book, the writer is the one telling the story.

Let's look at an example. A writer might tell the reader that a main character met her husband, got married, and then he was killed. But that is not enough. The writer should show the reader how much the husband loved his wife and how much she loved him. This helps the reader become involved in the story and feel bad when the husband dies.

The writer should add "meat" to the story. This means giving the reader more information about the characters and what they feel. For example, the writer could show how the husband and wife fell in love and how they were happy together. This would make the reader sad when the husband dies.

As a writer, it is hard to resist telling too much information. But it is not good to rush past important details. For example, a writer might want to tell the reader that a character used to be in the Air Force, works at a gas station, and has certain dreams. But the writer should only include the information that is important to the story.

I watched two news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was on NBC 4 this morning (August 13, 2011). The top story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio who hurt his wife. He is named Shad Hostettler. The news showed his picture. He looked very bad. They spent two minutes on this story. They said he hurt his wife many times and he was arrested.

The next story was about a shooting in the Sharon Woods area. A man named Travis Buyers was shot. He is 18 years old. He is very sick. The police are looking for the person who did it. This story was short. I think it was short because the man who was shot is black. I have noticed that the news does not always talk about crimes when the victim is black.

The news also talked about a helicopter that was shot. They found a hole in it. The police think it was shot with a .22 caliber bullet from a rifle. The police are looking for the person who shot the helicopter. They are offering a $5,000 reward for information that helps them catch the person.

The news also talked about the weather. They said it will be hot and rainy on Saturday. They said the temperature will be in the mid-80s all weekend.

The news also talked about a robbery at a store on Clime Road in Columbus. A black man with a hoodie robbed the store. He is tall and weighs about 150 pounds. They spent a lot of time saying the man was black.

The news also talked about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was a big drug dealer in Texas. He was caught and sentenced to 25 years in prison. They said he was a Hispanic man. I do not think that was important to the story.

There is a strong bond between brothers. This bond contains many emotions. These emotions include love, pride, anger, and sadness. Brothers understand each other better than anyone else. They can see themselves in their brother. When a situation is very bad, the true nature of this bond is clear. It can be good or bad. When brothers have strong feelings, there can be big costs. Understanding these feelings is hard. It means dealing with the bad things that come with them. When you look at a brother, you see your own reflection. You see yourself, not how others see you. Your actions and what happens because of them show your true character.

The story "The Scarlet Ibis" shows this theme. Two brothers go on a difficult journey. They have strong feelings of anger and pride. In a big moment, they have a bitter fight. Only one brother survives. The story tells us about the feelings of the brothers through direct descriptions of the main character, Doodle, and his brother. It also tells us through the narrator's point of view. This point of view shows the main character's feelings about the world and how they affect his actions.

The main character feels one main emotion: pride. He wants a brother who can do things with him. He wants a brother to be his friend. But his little brother, Doodle, is sick. Doodle cannot do the things the main character wants him to do. The main character has angry feelings towards Doodle. He even thinks about hurting Doodle. But when Doodle smiles, the main character feels love. This shows that the main character's love for his brother is strong. He wants to take care of Doodle and make him happy.

The human brain is a very complicated system. It helps us think and remember. Over time, people have used different ideas to explain how the brain works. 
- It was like a wax tablet at first.
- Then it was like a piece of paper.
- Then it was like a book.
- Now it is like a computer.

But these ideas are not very useful. They can lead to wrong conclusions. 
The brain gets information from our senses. Our senses are our eyes, ears, skin, and so on. They turn the world around us into signals that the brain can understand. The brain turns these signals into information that we can think about.

The brain uses two kinds of information processing. Bottom-up processing is like building a house. We start with small pieces and put them together to make something big. Top-down processing is like having a plan. We use what we already know to make something. For example, when we see a picture of a box, bottom-up processing helps us see that it is a box. Top-down processing helps us understand that it is a black box, not a hole.

The brain decides how important the information is. It also chooses which parts of the brain to use to think about it. This is called attention. For example, we can see many things when we look at the grass, but our brain does not make us think about them all. We might hear our name in a noisy room and understand what it means.

The brain has many stages of processing information. It also has different kinds of memory. We have sensory memory, working memory, and long-term memory. We store information and then we must keep it. There are different ways to store information, like seeing, hearing, or understanding. When we store information, we must keep it safe. Some research on animals shows that working memory is like a temporary signal that goes through the brain. Long-term memory is like a special kind of protein that helps us remember.

We have many ideas about how the brain organizes information. Some ideas come from how people remember things. Some ideas come from computers. Some ideas come from the way the brain works. One idea is that the brain is like a network. This network has many nodes, or points, that are connected. For example, the node for "chair" is connected to the node for "table." The node for "table" is connected to the node for "wooden."

Aldous Huxley criticizes the dangers of technology and capitalism in his book Brave New World. In the story, people value community over individuality and are taught to be happy from a young age. But the people are not free. They are controlled by a powerful leader called the World Controller. This story is like a warning about the problems of capitalism. 

Huxley uses ideas from a man named Karl Marx. Marx said that people are trapped in a system where they do not understand their place in society. In Brave New World, the people are taught what to think and what to do. They do not think for themselves. This is called false consciousness. The people are busy thinking about their own happiness, not about what is good for them.

The lower classes in the story are not allowed to be different from the others. They are taught to consume and spend money, but they do not know that they are being controlled. The people in charge, like the World Controller, are in control of everything. They make the rules and the people follow them. This is called hegemony. The people at the top are born into their position and do not think about changing the system. They are happy with their place in society.

In the story, people do not have deep relationships with each other. They do not feel strong emotions like love. They talk about physical things, like how people look. The people in the story do not question their place in society. They are happy to follow the rules and do what they are told. This shows how capitalism can control people and make them do what they want. 

Huxley is warning us about the dangers of a society that values technology and capitalism over individual freedom and happiness. He is saying that if we are not careful, we will lose our freedom and become like the people in Brave New World.

I am a student at University Park. I have been here for two and a half years. Getting around campus can be hard. My freshman year, I lived in a dorm room in East Halls, very far from the center of campus. To get to class in the Willard building, I had to walk 25 minutes. The weather was often bad, making it even harder.

I talked to a friend who rides a bike. He said, "Bikes are great. It's the best way to get around." Bicycling is good for your body and is the fastest way to travel. Eating a meal and biking can take you 30 miles or more.

I now live off campus, far from the center of campus. Buying a bike was a smart choice. I go to class in the Thomas building every day. Walking would take 25 minutes. But biking takes only 5 minutes if I pedal fast.

Walking has its advantages. But I am too busy to walk. If I didn't have a bike, walking would be my only way to get to class. Walking to Thomas every day would take 30-40 minutes. That's over two hours a week. I don't have time for that.

I think the best solution for getting around campus is to use a bike. If students ride bikes and the campus is built for bicyclists, we can solve the problem of mobility.
